overview: On March 24th Impact Wrestling presents Sacrifice 2023 live on FITE from Windsor, Ontario. The event will feature top IMPACT Wrestling stars such as IMPACT World Champion Josh Alexander, Knockouts Champion Mickie James, Tag Team Champions The Bullet Club, X-Division Champion Trey Miguel, Digital Media Champion Joe Hendry, plus Moose, Frankie Kazarian, Rich Swann, Eddie Edwards, Jonathan Gresham, The Motor City Machine Guns, Heath, Rhino, The Major Players, Deonna Purrazzo, Jordynne Grace and many more.
title: Impact Wrestling Sacrifice 2023
